# Monk

## Class Overview
**Role:** Mobile skirmisher, striker  
**Primary Ability Score(s):** Dexterity, Wisdom  
**Power Fantasy:** Mastery of body and spirit through disciplined training and inner energy  
**Design Notes:** Resource-driven martial class with short-rest recovery and strong action economy control

---

